{"tid":1002372,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機模擬景深影相","createTime":"2019-01-31T01:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T06:34:35.000Z","uid":79646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a22db31a413486c43c73025227c7b74e7deb2680","tid":1002372,"uid":79646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"點解我用samsung ， 用景深mode 要用遠攝鏡做影相? 明明近攝個鏡頭靚好多<br />\n<br />\n我見iphone 7+ 都係用近攝鏡影，遠攝鏡幫手分析做景深，所以iphone 景深無咁多noise<br />\n<br />\n其他android 機都係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8c31f2847e9e066191e0da6661eb893328b79f","tid":1002372,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"用近攝鏡影，遠攝鏡幫手分析做景深<br />\n<br />\n咁咪即係software扮景深，唔係hardware真係影出景深囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d027749afc7add6c276dc1ea979db833dcc8d1c5","tid":1002372,"uid":89350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"XR話左比你聽係假啦,單鏡咪一樣可調校的景深"},{"pid":"a97ebb5ffe0838c4e0aa9a2c079f1c5c63e98fb9","tid":1002372,"uid":34213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知算唔算叫景深<br />\n將啲野整矇就叫景深sosad"},{"pid":"324a74baf5ed742cb157279aa881b7ce2bad384a","tid":1002372,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"用Google Camera啦"},{"pid":"cbb30ab566382ae3bc26a42a9a159e6a4c4f30b9","tid":1002372,"uid":79646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f8c31f2847e9e066191e0da6661eb893328b79f","tid":1002372,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"用近攝鏡影，遠攝鏡幫手分析做景深<br />\n<br />\n咁咪即係software扮景深，唔係hardware真係影出景深囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"我一早都話模擬景深。<br />\n但唔明點解samsung 唔用近攝鏡頭個張做後製，而用遠攝鏡頭做後製。因為遠攝鏡多noise, 後製出黎都唔黎。"},{"pid":"cb73adca356bb92639d45a7a177c3018bbaa0de9","tid":1002372,"uid":79646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a97ebb5ffe0838c4e0aa9a2c079f1c5c63e98fb9","tid":1002372,"uid":34213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知算唔算叫景深<br />\n將啲野整矇就叫景深sosad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"我問題係點解唔用近攝鏡影出黎做後製。iphone 都會。唔好針對景深呢2個字。<br />\n我想知係咪用近攝鏡黎模擬做景深技術高d?<br />\n其他android 又係咪咁?<br />\n我自己本身都幾滿意部note9 影相，但個模擬景深用遠鏡取景，個效果仲差過部iphone7+"},{"pid":"4d26903b4320c7abbe31ebe0d92dd5c69595a27b","tid":1002372,"uid":28061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"因為iPhone 人像mode都係用zoon鏡黎影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc432ce26c9b6da290f0322d32172e2813316758","tid":1002372,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"iphone 夜景人像用tele鏡仲多noise  過xr夜景人像mode(假淺景深)"},{"pid":"08f46a722d850672c3e5fca062d6b84574777251","tid":1002372,"uid":79646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d26903b4320c7abbe31ebe0d92dd5c69595a27b","tid":1002372,"uid":28061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"因為iPhone 人像mode都係用zoon鏡黎影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"但我用屋企人部iphone 好似唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 其實我都係想note 9 人像mode 少d noise, 佢用zoom 鏡影既相做假淺景深，室內已經好多noise。<br />\n諗唔明點解唔用大光圈個鏡頭幅相整。"}]}